            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">SEVERAL OF THEM WRITTEN IN 1726.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">IX. ON SEEING VERSES WRITTEN UPON WINDOWS AT INNS.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-400-14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-1" n="1">T<hi rend="small-caps">HE</hi> sage, who said he should be proud</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-2" n="2">Of windows in his breast,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-3" n="3">Because he ne'er a thought allow'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-4" n="4">That might not be confes't;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-5" n="5">His window scrawl'd by every rake,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-6" n="6">His breast again would cover,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-7" n="7">And fairly bid the devil take</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-14W2-line-8" n="8">The diamond and the lover.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
